WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.199 --> 00:00:02.525
Well, good evening family.

00:00:02.525 --> 00:00:05.029
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:09.303 --> 00:00:09.920
I am just going to pray for a little bit before President Trump gives his speech.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:31.546
I felt to pray for him, for his mind to be clear, for him to say the things that are on his heart, not just what he wants to do for the nation, but that we would pray for him, that he would have clarity of thought and that there would be no interruption from the demonic.

00:00:32.986 --> 00:00:36.559
The spiritual warfare, I am sure, is very intense on such a speech.

00:00:37.479 --> 00:00:40.239
The nations are watching is what I am trying to say.

00:00:40.239 --> 00:00:42.200
There is a glare on my lens tonight.

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.714
I wonder what that is.

00:00:45.248 --> 00:00:45.552
That is weird.

00:00:45.552 --> 00:00:49.066
