00:00:49.066 --> 00:00:49.671
Maybe.

00:01:00.080 --> 00:01:00.240
It makes my eye show in that lens.

00:01:00.240 --> 00:01:01.039
And that is strange.

00:01:04.387 --> 00:01:04.773
I do not like looking at my eyeballs.

00:01:04.773 --> 00:01:08.580
Looking at my eyeballs as I am looking at that is creepy.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:15.040
I am trying to duck out of it.

00:01:20.013 --> 00:01:22.307
I do not want to look at it.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:24.020
Okay, keep looking.

00:01:24.020 --> 00:01:25.540
Is he gone?

00:01:25.540 --> 00:01:26.150
Yeah.

00:01:26.610 --> 00:01:27.759
I do not see me anymore.

00:01:29.862 --> 00:01:32.400
I think it is the way it was angled.

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:38.274
Thanks, I appreciate that.

00:01:38.274 --> 00:01:39.600
Let us see.

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:40.440
Okay, fix it.

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:40.860
Good.

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:46.960
I do not see me anymore.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:47.849
Well, okay.

00:01:47.849 --> 00:01:53.097
So, let us go over some of the things I saw last time really quickly.

00:01:53.097 --> 00:02:09.719
Yesterday, I told Diana, I said, "It is fun because whenever you are so open about everything that we go through, because the Lord said, Brandon, I want you to teach my people by example of how you got there, how I go into the throne room, and how I sit with him.

00:02:11.702 --> 00:02:34.879
" And regardless if people want to believe it or not, I want to tell you all, I know I am not perfect by any means, but I feel like of anybody that I have ever watched on YouTube, I do not see much of it, but I can tell you of two or three people that I know have a real close relationship with the Father.

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:45.760
And I always come at it saying it like this to be as humble as you can, because he resists the proud.

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:49.840
But whenever I tell you I see angels and I see what I see, how do I say that?

00:02:49.840 --> 00:03:00.239
It is more real to me than my son sitting across the table right here with his computer.

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:04.440
The supernatural is more real to me than the natural.

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:17.200
And whenever the Lord talks to me and I have these conversations, he says, "Brandon, I want you to teach people prayer.

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:35.680
I want you to teach them how to dip in the rivers, how to flow with my spirit.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:43.012
You are a forerunner to what is about to happen with this next move in the glory.

00:03:46.180 --> 00:03:50.720
" A voice crying in the wilderness telling them what is coming, they must be prepared.

00:03:50.720 --> 00:04:12.453
So in doing so, my method maybe is not always the best method, but it is stripping myself away of any pride, of any kind of self-exhortation of trying to make myself, it is like humble yourself underneath the mighty hand of God.

00:04:30.773 --> 00:04:31.280
And that is the bottom line.

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:57.600
What I am telling you when I read these books like this, the only way you are ever going to go to the greater glory is to be refined, being a janitor for 15 years, raising a child with special needs, doing the things that it takes to really tell your flesh to shut up when it comes to certain areas right now.

00:04:57.600 --> 00:05:15.760
Obviously, I have certain things to work on, but as I work on it and I go from glory to glory, entering into his presence is, I do not want to say it is an algorithm because that is disrespectful because you know, God is not going to be put in a box.

00:05:15.760 --> 00:05:18.320
But you enter into his presence with thanksgiving and worship.

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:20.160
You enter in by the word.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:23.120
You enter in by just being real.

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:29.342
There is so much charismatic Hollywood that the Lord said, "I am done with it.

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:38.409
" And I have tried so hard to tell you what is on his heart for what I hear.

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:44.764
And I only hear in part and sing in part.

00:05:44.764 --> 00:05:46.542
God is vast.

00:05:46.542 --> 00:05:49.820
Brandon Biggs only gets a little bitty glimpse.

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:01.048
And the little glimpse I get will change your life forever like it has done me when you have these visitations and the manifestations in my house around me in the car.

00:06:02.432 --> 00:06:10.219
And I try to always cultivate his presence by making it easy for him to feel comfortable in my home.

00:06:17.383 --> 00:06:18.400
Like I said, the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart who is perfect towards him.

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:26.720
And I think what does it take?

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:30.790
What does that look like?

00:06:30.790 --> 00:06:37.1000
What does it take to be like David, a man after his own heart?

00:06:37.1000 --> 00:06:44.280
So, I look at David and what the Bible tells us about David.

00:06:45.577 --> 00:07:11.759
And I look at the ones that he called friends like Abraham and I say, if that is what he called a friend, how do I mirror myself off of not all the bad things they did, but what was the good that I can see in the glimpse of just these pages right here?

00:07:15.066 --> 00:07:20.506
And I say if this is what he was looking for and he says, "Man, that made me happy," when it talks about being the apple of his eye.

00:07:21.931 --> 00:07:36.107
And Kathryn Kuhlman I looked at as a woman as a pioneer of her day and there are people that don't like Kathryn Kuhlman, I really do not care what you like, she has changed my life.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:50.514
I watch her videos and she is a woman of course, but she was a woman in a time frame in the 50s or whatever, 40s that it was not popular to be a woman preacher.

00:07:50.514 --> 00:08:05.599
Still they try to persecute you now, but Joyce Meyer and people like that have paved the way more for females to be able to speak like Nancy Dufresne and people like that.

00:08:05.599 --> 00:08:14.622
Sister Billy, you know, and it was not always popular and sometimes it is still not in some circles, but she was a pioneer.

00:08:14.622 --> 00:08:16.160
Sister Woodworth-Etter, Amy Semphle McPherson.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:25.840
And I think about what was it like to see the first person fall out in the spirit and people try to explain it away as something that they had never seen before.

00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:36.460
What was it like to see it when she touched them and they fell out and everybody is like, "That is witchcraft.

00:08:36.460 --> 00:08:38.436
" Instantaneously, there is a devil behind that.

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:45.550
And they are healed by the power of God.

00:08:45.550 --> 00:08:53.371
Because what you cannot explain, the church automatically throws rocks at it and they try to kill it.

00:08:53.371 --> 00:08:55.540
They do not cultivate it.

00:08:55.540 --> 00:09:06.533
She did not have anybody, I am sure, to call up on the phone, similar to what I do not a lot.

00:09:06.533 --> 00:09:12.711
You are doing something that is never been done before.

00:09:12.711 --> 00:09:13.618
Pioneer work.

00:09:13.618 --> 00:09:28.667
Seeing in the spirit like this and putting it on a live broadcast, I do not see anybody else doing it.

00:09:28.667 --> 00:09:37.977
And I am not trying to pat myself on the back, but the Lord said, "Brandon, be a forerunner to the next move.

00:09:37.977 --> 00:09:55.920
" When I told you I saw the chariots of fire when I was with Jesus in heaven and I was on the edge of heaven and Jesus was standing next to me and he said, "Do you see?

00:10:18.667 --> 00:10:19.253
" I said, "Lord, what are all those chariots of fire?

00:10:37.809 --> 00:10:38.299
" There were angels that look like chariots.

00:10:38.299 --> 00:10:45.623
They were on these chariots and the fire was behind them.

00:10:45.623 --> 00:10:49.420
The horses were in front that were beautiful.

00:10:49.420 --> 00:11:02.270
And these angels had this armor on and they had gifts that were all on the back that were like presents that had bows on them.

00:11:14.969 --> 00:11:15.640
It was symbolic.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:19.635
And I said, "Lord, what are those?

00:11:33.919 --> 00:11:34.159
" He said, "Those are end-time mantles.

00:11:34.159 --> 00:11:48.360
Those are end-time giftings that have never been seen before on this earth for the last outpouring, for I am going to do something new that has never been done before.

00:11:52.360 --> 00:12:00.880
" I thought about a lot as I have had these visitations really what he was saying and he said that that is yours right there as the chariots of fire.

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:11.760
On December the 25th of 2024, he spoke to me and he said, "I am giving out the gifts.

00:12:14.160 --> 00:12:27.587
" And I saw those chariots of fire going all throughout the world and they were dropping them on people and they floated down and that cloak that I always talk about comes on people.

00:12:28.500 --> 00:12:29.950
And he said, "You will cultivate this.

00:12:29.950 --> 00:12:31.260
Cultivate my presence.

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:42.284
" And as I saw the chariots of fire moving around, not all people got their gift because they were not ready for it.

00:12:47.051 --> 00:12:52.720
And some of the chariots of fire went back with the presence that they had because the people had not refined.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:55.060
They had not died and you did not qualify.

00:12:55.060 --> 00:12:57.040
People try to fast-track microwave to the anointing.

00:12:57.040 --> 00:13:05.668
They want to be the microwave.

00:13:05.668 --> 00:13:12.519
They want to be the one that's cut in line.

00:13:14.079 --> 00:13:14.693
And there's no line cutting.

00:13:17.839 --> 00:13:18.047
It comes by refining, and there is no microwave.

00:13:19.088 --> 00:13:20.880
It is a slow cooker that cooks over time from glory to glory.

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:21.920
He's changing us.

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:29.823
Whenever I bring these things to you, what I'm trying to say is I go back to elders that were forerunners like Jack Cole Roberts.

00:13:29.823 --> 00:13:33.999
Kim Clement is not here anymore.

00:13:33.999 --> 00:13:36.880
John Paul Jackson is not here anymore.

00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:45.940
I look at people that walked in different giftings that were very polished and really good at it.

00:13:45.940 --> 00:13:47.100
They were yielded.

00:14:02.420 --> 00:14:02.750
I think about how God used them and they went home.

00:14:02.750 --> 00:14:07.920
A lot of these men and women of God didn't live past 60.

00:14:08.439 --> 00:14:10.491
I don't understand all that.

00:14:21.820 --> 00:14:22.360
But I'm going to tell you this again: He will share his glory with no one.

00:14:22.360 --> 00:14:25.611
We are to attract, to deflect.

00:14:25.611 --> 00:14:36.960
As I try to tell you about books like this, this is how I try so hard to find him on a more intimate level than I already have found him.

00:14:42.959 --> 00:14:43.313
I say, I know there's more.

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:57.577
I say it all the time.

00:14:57.577 --> 00:15:00.320
Lord, I know there's more.

00:15:00.320 --> 00:15:02.959
I've barely touched this.

00:15:02.959 --> 00:15:24.940
If the angels can go around your throne and say, 'Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts throughout eternity,' and they keep seeing something new about you, it's not something that they're doing because it's just fun to do.

00:15:24.940 --> 00:15:30.026
They're seeing something new about the Father that they never knew existed every single time.

00:15:30.026 --> 00:15:41.223
They saw a new glimpse of his holiness and the awe of God, the splendor, the majesty of who he is.

00:15:41.600 --> 00:15:47.599
That's why I try so hard to have my spiritual thermostat, Diana and I both, checked all the time.

00:15:47.599 --> 00:15:51.549
What makes me go from glory to glory, the refining?

00:15:53.020 --> 00:16:00.141
I told him, I said, 'I'm not satisfied with where I'm at.

00:16:14.116 --> 00:16:14.507
Where is the next level?

00:16:14.507 --> 00:16:17.170
Persecution comes with it.

00:16:17.170 --> 00:16:20.150
Yeah, I know.

00:16:20.160 --> 00:16:21.669
Well, what does it take?

00:16:21.669 --> 00:16:22.640
' Not always.

00:16:28.106 --> 00:16:50.740
I told Braden, I said, 'In my curiosity, I'm saying don't let me taste it yet until I can see it, because I don't know if I really truly want it in the natural, because I know what it took to get where I'm at and the relationship that I have, and it has come out of very, very hard times.

00:16:50.740 --> 00:16:58.480
' I always test it, and the Lord said, 'Let me tell you, this right here, this book right here, my wife came.

00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:02.419
' The Lord spoke to me about being offended by things.

00:17:02.419 --> 00:17:14.410
