00:18:34.672 --> 00:18:36.731
I say that all the time because it's so true.

00:18:36.731 --> 00:18:46.026
'Depart from me, I never knew you,' is what he'll say to all.

00:18:46.026 --> 00:18:49.679
For wide is the way that leads to destruction.

00:18:49.679 --> 00:18:55.280
Big path, little path to him.

00:18:55.280 --> 00:18:58.773
Big path to destruction and to the devil.

00:18:58.773 --> 00:19:00.448
Little path to him.

00:19:00.448 --> 00:19:04.000
