00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:05.644
Are you on it?

00:19:05.644 --> 00:19:07.476
Be real with yourself tonight.

00:19:07.476 --> 00:19:12.720
That's what I try to be real with myself all the time.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:13.840
Strip yourself down.

00:19:13.840 --> 00:19:15.543
Am I really fooling myself?

00:19:15.543 --> 00:19:22.137
