00:19:22.137 --> 00:19:23.872
Because that's pride.

00:19:23.872 --> 00:19:24.640
Strip.

00:19:24.640 --> 00:19:34.470
Show people your vulnerable side so that they're able to learn from it.

00:19:34.480 --> 00:19:45.640
If I can find somebody that's real on YouTube than all the sugarcoated crap that I see, Hollywood Christianity, show me how to get there.

00:19:45.640 --> 00:19:47.947
Show me how to walk with him.

00:19:51.389 --> 00:19:53.140
