00:20:17.063 --> 00:20:21.147
Better than what I was gonna say.

00:20:21.147 --> 00:20:23.440
That's just flesh.

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:24.491
It's real though.

00:20:25.280 --> 00:20:27.760
