00:21:03.306 --> 00:21:08.960
' But I honor the position that you're walking in.

00:21:08.960 --> 00:21:12.320
I honor the position because God put you there.

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:26.023
Saul was one that David had all right to be really ticked off at and could have killed him several times, but he didn't and honored the anointing on his life.

00:21:28.257 --> 00:21:28.453
And he said, 'I will touch not the anointed.

00:21:28.453 --> 00:21:38.880
' He had every right to kill him right there in that cave and all the other times because he could have, but he feared God.

00:21:59.039 --> 00:21:59.261
I thought it's not about it; it's because God did it, so I honor the position.

00:22:03.884 --> 00:22:04.187
But I want to learn.

00:22:04.187 --> 00:22:23.086
I want to grab a hold of it and you pull yourself up and you keep crawling because it's all about having relationship with him in the ultimate.

00:22:23.086 --> 00:22:28.411
When it's all done, I'm going to stand before him and give an account for everything I've done, and I fear him.

00:22:37.919 --> 00:22:45.600
But if all of it was to go away today, I'm still going to pursue him just like I always have because my relationship has just been a pursuit since I was 16 years old.

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:55.131
