00:25:54.255 --> 00:25:59.440
But I can't be distracted with who's here and who's not.

00:25:59.440 --> 00:26:08.920
At the same time, I want you to get it so bad because we're running out of time.

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:10.720
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:26:10.720 --> 00:26:17.139
That's a different level: to escape the judgment, to escape the things, is having your lamp full of oil.

00:26:17.139 --> 00:26:20.490
