00:27:30.909 --> 00:27:33.959
I want to be the virgin with my lamp full.

00:27:49.679 --> 00:27:49.908
And you can argue with me all you want to, but I'm telling you what I feel in my heart, what the word says.

00:27:49.908 --> 00:27:51.050
Keep your lamp full.

00:27:51.050 --> 00:27:53.440
